description:
  Making JavaDoc comments more readable by:<br>
  <li> Hiding(folding) HTML tags;
  </li><li> Unescape HTML escaped chars;
  </li><li> Text styles for value of tags: &lt;code&gt; | &lt;tt&gt; | &lt;li&gt; | &lt;b&gt; | &lt;i&gt; | &lt;a href/name=...&gt; | @code | @literal | @link | @linkplain | @value;
  </li><li> Tag and tag's value text styles are customisable at Settings -&gt; Editor -&gt; Color Scheme -&gt; JavaDoc Clean Read. <br><br>

 Plugin is <b>paid</b> for commercial IDEs: IntelliJ IDEA Ultimate. <br>
 Plugin is <b>free</b>(for now) for community/free IDEs: IntelliJ IDEA Community, Android Studio. <br><br>

</li>
